<p>The following Excel Spreadsheets were developed by our team for our own engineering work. We are open-sourcing these calculators for public use to enable others to design safe, and reliable systems. <strong>Please note that these calculators come with reccomended reading resources, that we HIGHLY reccomend you review before using these calculators.</strong></p>

<p><a href="/calculators/bolt_calculator_v1-1.xlsx">Bolted Joint Calculator</a> <i class="fa-brands fa-creative-commons"></i></p>

<p><a href="/calculators/slips_and_fits_v1-1.xlsx">Slip + Interference Fits</a> <i class="fa-brands fa-creative-commons"></i></p>

